1. e4 {Endspiel-CD} c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Nc6 6. Bc4 Qb6 7. Nxc6 bxc6 8. O-O e5 9. Bg5 Qxb2 10. Qd3 Qb6 11. Bxf6 gxf6 12. Nd5 Qd8 13. Rab1 $5 $146 {This move looks like an improvment over Topalov's move (see game below).} (13. Ne3 Bh6 14. Rad1 Ke7 15. Bb3 Be6 16. Nc4 d5 17. Ba4 Rc8 18. Qa3+ c5 19. exd5 Bg4 20. f3 Bf5 21. d6+ Kf8 22. d7 Rc7 23. Rd5 Kg7 24. Nd6 Bxd7 25. Rfd1 Qe7 26. Bxd7 Qxd7 27. Qd3 Qe6 28. Qe4 Kg8 29. Nf5 {1-0 Topalov,V-Gavrikov,V/Geneva CS 1996}) 13... Be7 $1 (13... cxd5 $2 14. Qxd5 Be6 15. Bb5+ Ke7 16. Qb7+ Bd7 17. Bxd7 $18) (13... Be6 $2 14. Rb7 $1) (13... Bh6 14. Qf3 $5 cxd5 $2 15. Bxd5 Be6 (15... Bd7 16. Qh5) (15... Ba6 16. Qh5 O-O 17. Qxh6 Bxf1 18. Rb3) 16. Bxe6 fxe6 17. Qh5+ $18) 14. Nxe7 (14. Ne3 $5) 14... Kxe7 15. f4 Qa5 16. Kh1 Rg8 17. Bxf7 $6 {Since this move doesn't win by force , it better been avoided .} (17. f5 $5 $16) 17... Kxf7 18. Qxd6 Qd8 $1 19. Qxc6 Qd2 $1 20. Rg1 Bd7 21. Qc4+ Ke7 22. fxe5 fxe5 23. Rbd1 Qa5 24. Qd3 (24. Rd5 Be6 $1 $40) 24... Qc7 25. Qa3+ Ke8 26. Rgf1 $6 Rc8 27. Rd2 Qc4 $5 28. Rdf2 Qc5 29. Qf3 Kd8 (29... Qe7 $2 30. Qh5+ Rg6) 30. Rd2 Kc7 $1 (30... Rc7) (30... Rg7 $1 $16) 31. Rxd7+ $1 $14 Kxd7 32. Qf7+ Kc6 33. Rf6+ Kb5 34. Qb7+ Qb6 $6 {In this sort of endgames the defenders king is better placed on the first (or seventh) rank . Black is probably not familiar wit that secret .} 35. Rxb6+ axb6 36. Qd5+ Ka6 37. h3 Rg6 38. Qd3+ Kb7 39. Qd7+ Rc7 40. Qd5+ Ka7 41. c4 Rcg7 42. Qd2 Rg3 43. Qf2 Kb7 44. Kh2 Rxg2+ $142 45. Qxg2 Rxg2+ 46. Kxg2 Kc6 47. Kg3 Kc5 48. Kg4 Kxc4 49. Kf5 Kd4 50. h4 {Now , the bad position of the black king is felt !} b5 51. h5 b4 52. h6 Kc3 53. Kxe5 Kb2 54. Kf6 Kxa2 55. e5 b3 56. e6 b2 57. e7 b1=Q 58. e8=Q Qd3 59. Kg7 Ka3 60. Kh8 Qf5 61. Kg8 Qd3 62. Qf7 Ka4 (62... Kb2) 63. Kh8 Qe4 64. Qa7+ Kb5 65. Qxh7 Qe5+ 66. Qg7 Qe8+ 67. Kh7 Qe4+ 68. Qg6 Qe7+ 69. Kg8 Qd8+ (69... Ka4 $11 {Endspiel-CD} 70. h7 Qd8+ 71. Kg7 Qe7+ 72. Kh6 Qh4+ $11) 70. Kg7 Qe7+ 71. Qf7 Qe5+ (71... Qg5+ $11 {Endspiel-CD} 72. Kh7 (72. Qg6 Qe7+ $11) 72... Ka4 $11 (72... Qg1 $11)) 72. Qf6 Qg3+ 73. Kf7 Qc7+ (73... Qd3 $142 {Endspiel-CD} 74. Qf4 $1 $18 (74. Qg6 Qc4+ 75. Qe6 Qd3 76. Kg7 $18 {53}) (74. Kg7 $4 Ka4 $11) 74... Z0 75. Kg7 $140 Qd7+ 76. Kg6 (76. Qf7 $4 Qg4+ $11) 76... Qe8+ 77. Qf7 Qc6+ 78. Qf6 Qe8+ 79. Kg5 Qe3+ 80. Qf4 Qe7+ 81. Kg4 Qe2+ 82. Kf5 Qc2+ 83. Qe4 Qf2+ 84. Ke5 Qh2+ 85. Qf4 Qb2+ (85... Qh5+ 86. Kf6 $18) 86. Ke6 Qa2+ 87. Kf6 Qa6+ 88. Kg5 Qb7 89. Qf1+ Kc5 90. Qf5+ Kc4 91. h7 $18) 74. Kg6 Ka4 75. h7 Qg3+ 76. Kh5 (76. Kh5 {Endspiel-CD} Qh3+ $140 77. Qh4+) 1-0


