1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. g3 d5 4. Bg2 Be7 5. Nf3 O-O 6. O-O c6 7. Qc2 b6 8. Nc3 Nbd7 9. e4 Ba6 10. b3 Rc8 11. Rd1 Bb7 (11... dxc4 12. Bf4 b5 13. bxc4 bxc4 14. Qa4 Bb5 15. Nxb5 cxb5 16. Qxb5 Nxe4 17. Rac1 Nb6 18. Ne5 Nd6 19. Qa6 Rc7 20. Nc6 Qd7 21. d5 exd5 22. Nxe7+ Qxe7 23. Bxd5 Rd7 24. Re1 Qf6 25. Bc6 Rc7 26. Bg2 Re7 27. a4 Nf5 28. Rxe7 Qxe7 29. a5 Qa3 30. Qxa7 Nc8 31. Qc7 Ncd6 32. Bd5 Nb5 33. Qxc4 Qxa5 34. Bxf7+ Kh8 35. Qc5 Qd8 36. Bg5 Qb8 37. Bf4 Qd8 38. Qxf5 Nd4 39. Qg4 Qa8 40. Bh5 {1-0 Tosic,M-Kalezic,B/Subotica 2000/CBM 76 (40)}) 12. e5 Ne8 13. h4 Nc7 14. Ng5 Bxg5 15. hxg5 c5 16. dxc5 Nxc5 17. f4 Qe7 18. Ba3 Rfd8 19. Bf3 Ba8 20. Rd2 $1 {With a vicious and obvious idea!} dxc4 21. Rh2 $1 g6 22. Bxa8 cxb3 23. axb3 Nxa8 $2 (23... Rxa8 $142 24. Ne4 Nd5 {And though White is clearly better, there is no obvious crush - After the text, White wins quicly.}) 24. Ne4 Qb7 25. Nf6+ Kf8 26. Rxh7 Qf3 27. Kh2 Qe3 28. Rd1 {This 'only move', also completely wipes out blacks counterplay.} Qf3 29. Bxc5+ (29. Qxc5+ $1 bxc5 30. Bxc5+ $18 {"Ha, ha!" - Yudasin}) 1-0


